game.name: Barbie And The Pegasus
game.description:
You would notice a huge smile on the face of Barbie when you click the play button as she has planned to go outside with her beloved Pegasus. She has already made all the arrangements except selecting the outfit for the lady. Barbie is in hurry, so join Barbie And The Pegasus game and get ready to dress her up perfectly before their departure. Pegasus is already waiting for the girl outside, so it will be your responsibility to help the doll to pick up the nice outfit as fast as you can. 

Start with a right hairstyle and then come to the jewelry part in this brand new dressing game for girls! Give her a nice crown on her head and then pair it with a pair of lovely earrings and a lovely necklace on her neck! Choose a green color top with some work in red color or give your girl a blue color top with some silver work on its top part! Make sure to match your top with a blue color bottom or a green color bottom with some nice flair. 

You can also select a blue color frock or a red and pink color frock or a dress in a combination of yellow and purple color in this html5 princess dress-up game. Complete the look of your dress with a pair of red or blue color sandal or any color you want! Click the Reset button in case if you want to start your dress fun challenge from the scratch meanwhile! Feel free to click the show button to see the final outcome! Play more princess girls games online, no download required on atmegame.com!!
